      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPY TIPPY (1) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from nine starts. Comes off a (25.45) win last time, scoring by 2 lengths in a Grade 5 over 450m at this track. Has the ability and should feature. SANDAVE APACHE (8) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 450m behind Hand Me Down (26.29) in a Grade 5. Worth following up. GOLDSTAR KLEIN (2) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from four starts. Was out of the placings last time (26.17) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5, finishing eighth and beaten 8 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. NANGAR COUNTY (3) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
